status: MARC21-007: File formats of electronic resource
Whether the file(s) which comprise the electronic resource are of the same format or type for digitally reformatted materials.

definition (en): File(s) which comprise(s)the electronic resource are of the same format or type.
scope note (en): E.g., all .jpg; all .tif; all .txt; all .wav; all .mpg; etc.

definition (en): Files which comprise the electronic resource are of at least 2 different formats.
Format(s) of the file(s) which comprise(s) the electronic resource are not known.
